                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. He was brought to the watch-house.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw two young men behind the gentleman, they picked his pocket, and threw the handkerchief behind me.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220703-25-person268">
